title: Egypt: Minister - Unprecedented Boom in Economic Cooperation With Riyadh
text:
Kenya: Solar Power Installed at Dozens of Primary Schools 
Minister of Industry and Trade Mounir Fakhry Abdel Nour said that the coming period will witness a boom in relations between Egypt and Saudi Arabia in several fields. 
The Minister explained that the two countries are planning to take a number of measures to encourage trade exchange, joint investments and industrial integration thus taking advantage of the huge industrial bases in both countries. Egypt
